steps.step: Place the kale in a colander and run warm water over it while massaging the leaves until the kale softens.In a large bowl, combine the kale, cucumber, snap peas, tomatoes and quinoa. Toss with the dressing.
Serve.In a small glass bowl, whisk together the lemon juice, tahini, water and agave nectar. If the tahini is difficult to whisk, microwave the mixture on HIGH for about 10 seconds.
